source.name: Veterans Burial Sites
source.description: Gravesite locations of Veterans and beneficiaries includes burial records from many sources. These sources provide varied data; some searches may contain less information than others. Information on veterans buried in private cemeteries was collected for the purpose of furnishing government grave markers, and we do not have information available for burials prior to 1997.
